@contentType = application/json

### ========== PROJECTS ==========

### Get all projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects

### Get project by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}

### Get projects by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects?status=termine

### Create a new project
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
