### ========== SKILLS ==========

### Get all skills
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/skills

### Get skills by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/skills?category=Frontend

### Get skills grouped by categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/skills/by-categories

### Get skill by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/skills/{{skillId}}

### Create a new skill
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/skills
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "TypeScript",
  "category": "Frontend",
  "level": "advanced",
  "percentage": 85,
  "description": "Typage statique pour JavaScript",
